msgid "# Test-Dtc"
msgstr "# Test-Dtc"

msgid "## SYNOPSIS"
msgstr "## 概述"

msgid "Tests whether two computers can participate in networked transactions."
msgstr "测试两台计算机是否可以参与联网交易。"

msgid "## SYNTAX"
msgstr "## 语法"

msgid "## DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "## 说明"

msgid ""
"The **Test-Dtc** cmdlet tests whether two computers can participate in networked transactions.\n"
"The cmdlet performs the following tests:"
msgstr "`Test-Dtc` cmdlet 用于检测两台计算机是否可以参与网络交易。该 cmdlet 执行以下测试："

msgid ""
"To run this cmdlet, you must first enable the firewall rule for Distributed "
"Transaction Coordinator on both computers by using the Netsh utility run the"
" following command:"
msgstr ""
"要运行此 cmdlet，您必须首先使用 Netsh 工具在两台计算机上启用分布式事务协调器（Distributed Transaction "
"Coordinator）的防火墙规则，请运行以下命令："

msgid ""
"`netsh advfirewall firewall set rule group=\"Distributed Transaction "
"Coordinator\" new enable=yes`"
msgstr ""
"请帮我将以下命令转换为中文：  \n"
"`netsh advfirewall firewall set rule group=\"Distributed Transaction Coordinator\" new enable=yes`"

msgid ""
"For more information, see [Netsh Command Syntax, Contexts, and "
"Formatting](/windows-server/networking/technologies/netsh/netsh-contexts)."
msgstr ""
"有关更多信息，请参阅[Netsh命令语法、上下文和格式化](/windows-"
"server/networking/technologies/netsh/netsh-contexts)。"

msgid "To enable the rule using PowerShell run the following command:"
msgstr "要使用 PowerShell 启用该规则，请运行以下命令："

msgid ""
"`Enable-NetFirewallRule -DisplayGroup \"Distributed Transaction "
"Coordinator\"`"
msgstr ""
"`Enable-NetFirewallRule -DisplayGroup \"Distributed Transaction "
"Coordinator\"`"

msgid "## EXAMPLES"
msgstr "## 示例"

msgid "### Example 1: Test MSDTC on the local computer"
msgstr "### 示例 1：在本地计算机上测试 MSDTC"

msgid "This command tests MSDTC on the local computer."
msgstr "此命令用于测试本地计算机上的 MSDTC（Microsoft Distributed Transaction Coordinator）。"

msgid "### Example 2: Test MSDTC on the local computer and a remote computer"
msgstr "### 示例 2：在本地计算机和远程计算机上测试 MSDTC"

msgid ""
"This command tests the local computer and the computer named Contoso075.\n"
"The command specifies a resource manager port."
msgstr "这个命令用于测试本地计算机以及名为Contoso075的计算机。该命令指定了一个资源管理器端口。"

msgid ""
"### Example 3: Test MSDTC on a local computer that blocks inbound "
"transactions"
msgstr "### 示例 3：在阻止入站交易的本地计算机上测试 MSDTC"

msgid ""
"This command tests the local computer and the computer named Contoso075.\n"
"The output from this test shows that the local computer does not allow inbound transactions."
msgstr ""
"这个命令用于测试本地计算机和名为Contoso075的计算机。测试结果显示，本地计算机不允许接收入站数据传输（即不允许外部计算机向本地计算机发送数据）。"

msgid ""
"### Example 4: Test MSDTC on a local computer that blocks outbound "
"transactions"
msgstr "### 示例 4：在阻止出站交易的本地计算机上测试 MSDTC"

msgid ""
"This command tests the local computer and the computer named Contoso075.\n"
"The output from this test shows that the local computer does not allow outbound transactions."
msgstr ""
"此命令用于测试本地计算机以及名为“Contoso075”的计算机。测试结果显示，本地计算机不允许发起出站数据传输（即不允许数据从本地计算机发送到其他计算机）。"

msgid "## PARAMETERS"
msgstr "## 参数"

msgid ""
"Specifies the virtual server name of the MSDTC instance on the local "
"computer to test."
msgstr "指定要测试的本地计算机上MSDTC实例的虚拟服务器名称。"

msgid ""
"Specifies the virtual server name of the MSDTC instance on the remote "
"computer to test."
msgstr "指定用于测试的远程计算机上MSDTC实例的虚拟服务器名称。"

msgid ""
"Specifies the port number that the MSDTC diagnostic Resource Manager uses.\n"
"If you do not specify a value, this cmdlet uses a default value of 3002."
msgstr "指定 MSDTC 诊断资源管理器使用的端口号。如果您不指定值，此 cmdlet 将使用默认值 3002。"

msgid ""
"Shows what would happen if the cmdlet runs.\n"
"The cmdlet is not run."
msgstr "展示了如果运行该cmdlet会发生什么情况。但实际上并没有运行该cmdlet。"

msgid "Prompts you for confirmation before running the cmdlet."
msgstr "在运行该cmdlet之前，会提示您进行确认。"

